movie_name: Behind the Curtain: Stranger Things: The First Shadow
short_description: With special backstage access, see how the cast and crew of "Stranger Things: The First Shadow" race against time to prepare for this groundbreaking theater premiere in London's West End, amid public and critical expectations.
